https://news.sky.com/story/teen-suspected-of-plotting-taylor-swift-concert-attack-carried-out-concrete-preparatory-actions-13193116"><em>天空新闻</em></a>）。据报道，警方搜查了他的家，发现了化学品、爆炸物、刀具和砍刀。</p><p>据后来报道， <a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/third-teenager-arrested-over-taylor-swift-show-terror-plot-in-vienna-3782385">第三名嫌疑人在据称与主要嫌疑人接触后被该地区警方逮捕</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3784742" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3784742" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3784742" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 在温布利大球场举行的“Eras Tour”演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3784742" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特。图片来源：Gareth Cattermole/TAS24/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>上周，涉嫌恐怖阴谋的主要嫌疑人的代理律师<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyer-for-suspect-in-taylor-swift-vienna-terror-plot-says-accusations-are-exaggerated-3783655">声称，对其当事人的指控被夸大了</a>。辩护律师沃纳·托马内克说：“他既没有手段、也没有可能性，也没有炸药来实施这一行动。”他接着补充说，“所谓的袭击计划纯粹是幻想。”</p><p>鉴于这种情况<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/police-to-make-decisions-about-taylor-swifts-london-shows-following-vienna-terror-threat-3782048">，关于伦敦的演出是否会如期继续存在一些争论</a>，苏格兰场警方后来证实， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swifts-london-shows-not-impacted-by-vienna-terror-plot-confirm-met-police-3782211">温布利的剩余演出不应“受到维也纳恐怖阴谋的影响”</a> 。温布利的演出按计划进行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-changes-wembley-stage-times-following-foiled-vienna-terror-plot-3783073">但开始和结束时间比门票首次发售时最初宣布的时间要早</a>​​。</p><p>在她巡演的最后一场温布利体育场演出中，斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-florence-welch-and-jack-antonoff-join-taylor-swift-on-stage-at-wembley-stadium-3785394">邀请弗洛伦斯·韦尔奇和杰克·阿诺托诺夫作为特邀嘉宾登台</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-debuts-so-long-london-to-close-out-eras-shows-at-wembley-stadium-3785426">首演了《再见，伦敦》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-shares-behind-the-scenes-look-at-eras-tour-with-i-can-do-it-with-a-broken-heart-video-3785413">《我可以用破碎的心做到》的音乐录影带</a>来结束演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-comments-on-devastating-vienna-terror-plot-explains-her-silence-was-for-the-priority-of-fans-safety-3785802">泰勒·斯威夫特评论“毁灭性”维也纳恐怖阴谋的帖子，解释说她的“沉默”是为了歌迷安全的“优先”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
